    <item>
      <title>汇丰银行聘请丑闻缠身的三菱日联金融集团子公司销售武士债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/hsbc-hires-mufg-unit-to-sell-first-samurai-bond-in-5-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[香港上海汇丰银行已聘请三菱日联摩根士丹利证券公司作为主承销商，负责销售武士债券。此前，日本发行人因曝光不当商业行为而将该经纪公司排除在交易之外。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/hsbc-hires-mufg-unit-to-sell-first-samurai-bond-in-5-years</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 06:37:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>壳牌将收购新加坡液化天然气贸易商 押注需求旺盛</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/shell-to-buy-singaporean-lng-trading-firm-pavilion-energy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[壳牌公司同意收购液化天然气贸易商 Pavilion Energy Pte，这是该石油巨头对燃料需求将持续上升的最新押注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/shell-to-buy-singaporean-lng-trading-firm-pavilion-energy</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 06:00:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
